msgstr ""
"<strong>Aplikasi Appointment memungkinkan pemesanan mandiri, sinkronisasi "
"kalender, dan follow‑up mudah.</strong>"

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Our Consultation sheets record symptoms, vitals, and actions while "
"keeping the vet’s workflow fluid.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Lembar Konsultasi kami mencatat gejala, tanda-tanda vital, dan "
"tindakan yang dilakukan sekaligus memastikan alur kerja dokter tetap lancar."
"</strong>"

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Our POS lets receptionists scan, split bills, and print receipts—"
"while stock levels adjust instantly.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>POS memungkinkan resepsionis memindai, membagi tagihan, dan mencetak "
"nota—sementara stok barang diperbarui otomatis.</strong>"

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Our Pet records feature centralizes identity, vaccination status, "
"and allergies for safer treatments.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Fitur record Peliharaan kami merupakan pusat informasi identitas, "
"status vaksinasi, dan alergi untuk perawatan yang lebih aman.</strong>"

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Our Product management keeps pricing, barcodes, and expiry dates "
"accurate across sales channels.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Tim manajemen Produk kami memastikan harga, barcode, dan tanggal "
"kedaluwarsa tetap akurat di seluruh saluran sales.</strong>"

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Our Sales app groups treatments, products, and services into neat "
"documents owners trust.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Aplikasi Sales kami mengelompokkan perawatan, produk, dan layanan "
"menjadi dokumen rapi yang dipercayai pemilik.</strong>"

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Our Website app lets you publish pages, embed booking widgets, and "
"convert visitors into appointments.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Dengan aplikasi Website kami, Anda dapat menerbitkan halaman, "
"menyematkan widget pemesanan, dan mengubah pengunjung menjadi appointment.</"
"strong>"

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Owner relationship</strong> connects contact details for billing and "
"reminders."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Hubungan pemilik</strong> menyambungkan detail kontak untuk "
"penagihan dan pengingat."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Payment terms</strong> handle deposits, installments, or immediate "
"pay."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Termin pembayaran</strong> menangani setoran, angsuran, atau kontan."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Price lists &amp; promos</strong> support wellness plans or "
"discounted packages."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Daftar harga &amp; promosi</strong> mendukung rencana kesehatan atau "
"paket diskon."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Real‑time sync</strong> with accounting and inventory for zero "
"re‑entry."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Sinkronisasi real-time</strong> dengan akuntansi dan inventaris agar "
"bebas ada entri ulang."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Reorder rules</strong> trigger purchase orders before you run out."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Aturan order ulang</strong> memicu pembuatan purchase order otomatis "
"sebelum stok habis."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Revenue reporting</strong> reveals top services, margins, and "
"seasonal trends."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Laporan pendapatan</strong> mengungkapkan layanan teratas, margin, "
"dan tren musiman."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>SEO tools</strong> improve ranking so local pet owners find you "
"first."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Alat SEO</strong> meningkatkan peringkat agar Anda ditemukan lebih "
"dulu oleh pemilik hewan lokal."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Staff agenda integration</strong> syncs with Google, Outlook, and "
"mobile calendars."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Integrasi agenda staf</strong> terhubung dengan Google, Outlook, dan "
"kalender di smartphone."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Start small, iterate.</strong> Configure your website and "
"appointments first, then add your products to the mix, before managing your "
"consultations."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Sedikit demi sedikit, lama-lama jadi bukit.</strong> Mulailah dari "
"mengatur website dan appointment, lalu tambahkan produk sebelum mengelola "
"konsultasi Anda."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Template fields </strong>(vaccines, agression level, observed "
"ilnesses, etc.) speed up SOAP or problem‑oriented entries."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Field template </strong>(vaksin, keagresifan, penyakit yang diamati, "
"dll.) mempercepat entri berbasis SOAP atau masalah."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>The chatter </strong>can be used to track ongoing discussion about a "
"pet's consultation for record keeping."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Chatter </strong>dapat digunakan untuk melacak diskusi berjalan "
"tentang konsultasi hewan peliharaan untuk keperluan pencatatan record."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Touch interface</strong> optimized for tablets or desktop stations."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Antarmuka sentuh</strong> yang dioptimalkan untuk tablet atau "
"komputer desktop."

#. module: veterinary_clinic
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:veterinary_clinic.welcome_article_body
